# 100-CIMS Project Overview

## Project Structure
- `src/app`: Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- `src/components`: React components organized by category
- `src/components/ui`: Shadcn UI components (should rarely be edited)
- `src/lib`: Utility functions organized by category
- `src/types`: TypeScript type definitions
- `prisma`: Database schema and migrations
- `public`: Static assets

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Prisma for database access
- TailwindCSS for styling
- Shadcn UI components
- React Query for data fetching
- Mapbox for map interactions

## Coding Standards
- Follow project code style rules in 002-code-styles.mdc
- Maintain semantic HTML structure
- Ensure responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Use React Server Components when possible
- Follow proper error handling patterns
- Optimize for performance and accessibility
